ygData.messageBody:
Someone told me to make scalars (files) from skill level 20 to 40. So I ran and
bout all the file molds I could carry only to find that they were trivial to me. I
had to sell all the molds back to the NPC and make studs. This brings up the
question, is there a list of objects and their trivial level? Also, what is the
best thing to make at 23? I think my choices are:

Skewers
studs
lanterns

Any suggestions?

I would think that studs might be good if they can be sold to players, but I would
have no idea what studs would sell for.

Cerivolk - karana
